graphics.name: Amino sugar and nucleotide sugar metabolism

nodes.name: UDP-2,3-bis(3-hydroxytetradecanoyl)glucosamine:2,3-bis-(3-hydroxytetradecanoyl)-alpha-D-glucosaminyl-1-phosphate 2,3-bis(3-hydroxytetradecanoyl)-glucosaminyltransferase
nodes.rxn: UDP-2,3-bis(3-hydroxytetradecanoyl)glucosamine + Lipid X <=> UDP + Lipid A disaccharide

nodes.name: dodecanoyl-[acyl-carrier protein]:KDO2-lipid-IVA O-dodecanoyltransferase
nodes.rxn: Dodecanoyl-[acyl-carrier protein] + KDO2-lipid IVA <=> Lauroyl-KDO2-lipid IV(A) + Acyl-carrier protein

nodes.name: tetradecanoyl-[acyl-carrier protein]:dodecanoyl-KDO2-lipid IV(A) O-tetradecanoyltransferase
nodes.rxn: Tetradecanoyl-[acp] + Lauroyl-KDO2-lipid IV(A) <=> KDO2-lipid A + Acyl-carrier protein

nodes.name: lipid-IVB hydroxyacylhydrolase
nodes.rxn: Lipid IVB + H2O <=> Deacyl-lipid IVB + (R)-3-Hydroxymyristic acid

nodes.name: hexa-acylated-KDO2-lipid-A phosphohydrolase
nodes.rxn: H. pylori KDO2-lipid A + H2O <=> 1-Dephospho-KDO2-lipid A + Orthophosphate

nodes.name: 4'-dephosphorylated-1-PEtN-KDO-lipid-A acyloxyacylhydrolase
nodes.rxn: 4'-Dephosphorylated 1-PEtN-KDO-lipid A + H2O <=> H. pylori KDO-lipid A + (R)-3-(Tetradecanoyloxy)hexadecanoic acid

nodes.name: tetradecanoyl-[acyl-carrier protein]:octadecanoyl-KDO2-lipid-IVA O-tetradecanoyltransferase
nodes.rxn: Tetradecanoyl-[acp] + Stearoyl-KDO2-lipid IVA <=> H. pylori KDO2-lipid A + Acyl-carrier protein

nodes.name: octadecanoyl-[acyl-carrier protein]:KDO2-lipid-IVA O-octadecanoyltransferase
nodes.rxn: Octadecanoyl-[acyl-carrier protein] + H. pylori KDO2-lipid IVA <=> Stearoyl-KDO2-lipid IVA + Acyl-carrier protein

nodes.name: (9Z)-hexadec-9-enoyl-[acyl-carrier protein]:KDO2-lipid IVA O-palmitoleoyltransferase
nodes.rxn: Hexadecenoyl-[acyl-carrier protein] + KDO2-lipid IVA <=> (9Z)-Hexadec-9-enoyl-KDO2-lipid IV(A) + Acyl-carrier protein

nodes.name: tetradecanoyl-[acyl-carrier protein]:(9Z)-hexadec-9-enoyl-KDO2-lipid IVA O-tetradecanoyltransferase
nodes.rxn: Tetradecanoyl-[acp] + (9Z)-Hexadec-9-enoyl-KDO2-lipid IV(A) <=> Palmitoleoyl-myristoyl-KDO2-lipid A + Acyl-carrier protein

nodes.name: KDO2-lipid-A acyloxyacylhydrolase
nodes.rxn: KDO2-lipid A + H2O <=> 3'-O-Deacylated KDO2-lipid A + (R)-3-(Tetradecanoyloxy)tetradecanoic acid

nodes.name: phosphatidylethanolamine:Kdo2-lipid-A-1-(2-aminoethyl diphosphate) ethanolaminephosphotransferase
nodes.rxn: Phosphatidylethanolamine + Kdo2-lipid A 1-(2-aminoethyl diphosphate) <=> Diacylglycerol + Kdo2-lipid A 1,4'-bis(2-aminoethyl diphosphate)

nodes.name: 4-amino-4-deoxy-alpha-L-arabinopyranosyl ditrans,octacis-undecaprenyl phosphate:KDO2-lipid A 4-amino-4-deoxy-alpha-L-arabinopyranosyltransferase
nodes.rxn: KDO2-lipid A + Undecaprenyl phosphate alpha-L-Ara4N <=> alpha-Kdo-(2->4)-alpha-Kdo-(2->6)-[4-P-L-Ara4N]-lipid A + di-trans,poly-cis-Undecaprenyl phosphate

nodes.name: KDO2-lipid-A,2-oxoglutarate:oxygen oxidoreductase (ester-linked acyl 2-hydroxylase)
nodes.rxn: KDO2-lipid A + 2-Oxoglutarate + Oxygen <=> (S)-2-Hydroxymyristate-modified lipid A + Succinate + CO2

nodes.name: 4-amino-4-deoxy-alpha-L-arabinopyranosyl ditrans,octacis-undecaprenyl phosphate:lipid IVA 4-amino-4-deoxy-beta-L-arabinopyranosyltransferase
nodes.rxn: Undecaprenyl phosphate alpha-L-Ara4N + 2,3,2'3'-Tetrakis(3-hydroxytetradecanoyl)-D-glucosaminyl-1,6-beta-D-glucosamine 1,4'-bisphosphate <=> Lipid IIA + di-trans,poly-cis-Undecaprenyl phosphate

nodes.name: 4-amino-4-deoxy-alpha-L-arabinopyranosyl ditrans,octacis-undecaprenyl phosphate:lipid IVB 4-amino-4-deoxy-L-arabinopyranosyltransferase
nodes.rxn: Undecaprenyl phosphate alpha-L-Ara4N + Lipid IVB <=> Lipid IIB + di-trans,poly-cis-Undecaprenyl phosphate

nodes.name: ditrans,octacis-undecaprenyl-diphosphate:KDO2-lipid-A phosphotransferase
nodes.rxn: di-trans,poly-cis-Undecaprenyl diphosphate + KDO2-lipid A <=> di-trans,poly-cis-Undecaprenyl phosphate + KDO2-lipid A 1-diphosphate

nodes.name: phosphatidylethanolamine:Kdo2-lipid-A ethanolaminephosphotransferase
nodes.rxn: Phosphatidylethanolamine + KDO2-lipid A <=> Diacylglycerol + Kdo2-lipid A 1-(2-aminoethyl diphosphate)
